      <title>智利燃料林业巨头 Copec 探索绿色氢气和铜选项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/chilean-fuel-to-forestry-giant-copec-explores-green-hydrogen-and-copper-options</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着清洁能源转型推动需求，智利最大的工业集团 Empresas Copec SA 正在探索扩大绿色氢和铜矿开采的选择。]]></description>
